Articles.Content: Hi i am having an error message come up that says there is issues with b9partswitch. How do i upload my log etc?i have a bunch of mods installed. steam auto updated the game version and even after rolling it back to 1.7.3 i keep getting this issue. the box gives me an option to quit the game?
Issue has been solved this thread can be closed. Incompatible version of module manager and b9partswitch.
Thread closed at OP request.
